\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
code{RDDbw_IK()}
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 This function takes simply a RDDdata object as input, and returns the optimal
 value according to the MSE criterion.
 
\end_layout

